    <title>Essential Phone OTA With ROOT</title>
    <link href="https://smaxad47.github.io/wiki/Android/Essential%20Phone%20OTA%20With%20ROOT/"/>
    <id>https://smaxad47.github.io/wiki/Android/Essential Phone OTA With ROOT/</id>
    <published>2019-07-08T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-07-09T03:19:22.258Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Essential-Phone-OTA-With-ROOT"><a href="#Essential-Phone-OTA-With-ROOT" class="headerlink" title="Essential Phone OTA With ROOT"></a>Essential Phone OTA With ROOT</h1><h2 id="获取最新包"><a href="#获取最新包" class="headerlink" title="获取最新包"></a>获取最新包</h2><p><a href="https://www.essential.com/developer/current-builds" target="_blank" rel="noopener">获取最新的OTA包和FASTBOOT包</a><br>从FASTBOOT包中将BOOT取出，用Magisk给Boot打补丁<br>Or<br>从<a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1iayS6YHYZvqkD1Y8oYV3ewzW5aAPe8C2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>下载最新的Boot.img，用Magisk给Boot.img打补丁</p><h2 id="OTA"><a href="#OTA" class="headerlink" title="OTA"></a>OTA</h2><p>线耍OTA包<br><code>adb reboot recovery</code>进入<strong>recovery</strong>,或关机后按住音量+BOOTLOADER再进<strong>recovery</strong>。选择<strong>Apply update from ADB</strong>，<code>adb sideload OTAupdate.zip</code>完成版本升级，此时应已经升级完成，未有ROOT</p><h2 id="ROOT"><a href="#ROOT" class="headerlink" title="ROOT"></a>ROOT</h2><p><code>adb reboot bootloader</code>将打好补丁的Boot.img刷入Boot分区<br><code>fastboot flash boot_a/b magisk_patched.img</code>，暂时没有找到好的方法可以查看活动插槽，可以使用<code>fastboot flash boot XXX</code>来报错，查看当前插槽</p><h2 id="打补丁"><a href="#打补丁" class="headerlink" title="打补丁"></a>打补丁</h2><p>将原厂镜像放入手机，用Magisk安装-&gt;选择修补一个文件。</p>]]></content>
    
